{"tid":458502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國歌填詞人田漢昔日被鬥死 誰最不尊重國歌？","createTime":"2017-11-05T02:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T04:39:44.000Z","uid":19552,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7d319a551e57925d6dcbdb1980c24b296bfaae96","tid":458502,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T02:29:56.000Z","msg":"中國國歌《義勇軍進行曲》由田漢作詞、聶耳作曲，原本是抗日電影《風雲兒女》的主題曲，這首歌曲在國共內戰期間被國民黨禁播，1949年中共將《義勇軍進行曲》訂為暫定國歌。<br />\n<br />\n至文化大革命時期，田漢被批鬥，並於獄中被迫害至死。文化大革命期間禁播《義勇軍進行曲》的詞、只可以播放音樂，於公開場合則改唱《東方紅》。文化界於文化大革命後，為《義勇軍進行曲》集體填詞；直至1978年，中共正式將《義勇軍進行曲》訂立為國歌，翌年田漢亦獲得當局平反，國歌再改回田漢作詞、聶耳作曲版本的《義勇軍進行曲》。"},{"pid":"68a8d87c4ead898341da74cd0dc4d0234dabf9e0","tid":458502,"uid":36300,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T02:35:25.000Z","msg":"中國共產黨笑撚死人"},{"pid":"488a27167ddcb5d8843a75ccf574f548eb554bdd","tid":458502,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T02:36:19.000Z","msg":"最多都係不尊重中國國歌填詞人啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f25ffd52797bf2905c05e556a2e3b374063875f","tid":458502,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T02:41:26.000Z","msg":"終國：冇D咁既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e48fa01a9a93857452abbb9964c77780567810","tid":458502,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4c331e72991910fbb45bcdd40be08af8767c71","tid":458502,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:28:02.000Z","msg":"一件事還一件事<br />\n人可以唔尊重<br />\n但歌一定要尊重"},{"pid":"40f6a3228bcc212f14ea98a8d3bd6c0d9be83e91","tid":458502,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/121652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F121652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0c579d86&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71113da7ddcc98a0b0961d7bde89506fb2f1a9c8","tid":458502,"uid":7840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:39:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}